object

objects and each source correlithm object in a node
table

table with the shortest distance
fetch a target correlithm object in the node table
linked with the source correlithm object
output the target correlithm object
actor

correlithm object and each output correlithm
object in an actor table
identify an output correlithm object from the
actor table with the shortest distance
fetch a real world value in the actor table
linked with the output correlithm object
output the real world output value
